  result: resourcesCatalogueList(input: $input) {

    data {
      id

      organizationName
      classificationId
      classificationName
      updateDate

      districtNum

      fileTypes
      tags
      interfaceNum
      fileNum
      datasetNum
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
}
